{"tid":108670,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過海嵾威？","createTime":"2017-02-05T12:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T08:30:38.000Z","uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc49b22be4693bee18a0b6055ba2cc77b7585b7","tid":108670,"uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:16:37.000Z","msg":"旅費有限，又唔知點解一路都想去俄羅斯，所以打算近近地去海嵾威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知有咩要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48446205105ceb2a3d5437c98d39af8508674ee5","tid":108670,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"我去過，注意唔好望實d 女"},{"pid":"0ac838cb68ec2618991dd8afe796aa8a2f0463b4","tid":108670,"uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去過，注意唔好望實d 女</blockquote><br />\n因為會比佢地啲仔打柒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我係絲 所以應該唔會望女</span>"},{"pid":"4df7288fbfa730e070049c46427d0b53ab7076f7","tid":108670,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"記得講cyka blyat 同人問好"},{"pid":"c8e318b1293df8f2a64fa77abe523d25c1c059fa","tid":108670,"uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得講cyka blyat 同人問好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1cbd1cbf35377d055f9d97081cc26cb2650584","tid":108670,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"冇乜好注意<br />\n<br />\n算最易遊嘅俄羅斯城市<br />\n<br />\n只去海參崴唔洗去咁耐，景點少，食真係豐儉由人。<br />\n<br />\n好多鄰國人。"},{"pid"