es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知有冇咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba1980d7fe99e88f152b9334d93cf4b88805cba","tid":108670,"uid":30464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n俄航？"},{"pid":"9bc17179e452d55a0af1ca20fa520320d25fad82","tid":108670,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n俄航？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個月查到三千頭左右來回<br />\n<br />\n得俄航有直飛。"},{"pid":"a7a84e26624e447d10ca51d2f31b35577e6c6859","tid":108670,"uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n俄航？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個月查到三千頭左右來回<br />\n<br />\n得俄航有直飛。</blockquote><br />\n其實俄航服務點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好同差都聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5a5af525608bbd16340ab0ba98c4f1ad027e7d","tid":108670,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n俄航？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個月查到三千頭左右來回<br />\n<br />\n得俄航有直飛。</blockquote><br />\n其實俄航服務點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好同差都聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你錢多時間多咪坐中東三寶轉機過去。"},{"pid":"071aed5f02263978bfa09dd87f7c03c274cf5165","tid":108670,"uid":81402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"樓豬可以諗下Irkutsk 近近地又可以玩埋貝加爾湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42b6cb09a97199b25d23df9bbd461514388f13b","tid":108670,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得食俄妹？"},{"pid":"b5de83e835ab1d6ab300d50a451291c9c75217ba","tid":108670,"uid":23688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n其實我想搏盡啲 Moscow, St Petersburg, 波羅的海3國同Helsinki咁玩 橫掂都咁近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知有冇咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主預budget 幾多先 如果得幾千慳慳地玩moscow+st petersburg 應該無問題，呢排俄航做緊promote 你仲可以st petersburg 入moscow 走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0a745352535030db03600453b2648076618daa","tid":108670,"uid":23688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有得食俄妹？</blockquote><br />\n上次去moscow 問路，有兩個女仔勁熱情又帶路又問我有無拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臨走佢問我夜晚飲唔飲野我拒絕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起都後悔"},{"pid":"7440f10d26acc000889689e7771d20bb5a340004","tid":108670,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n俄航？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個月查到三千頭左右來回<br />\n<br />\n得俄航有直飛。</blockquote><br />\n其實俄航服務點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好同差都聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俄航呢，機上娛樂同服務唔算好，但唔係差咁。餐食算ok。不過聽聞就係好多機司以前都係空軍，飛得好粗魯。"},{"pid":"b72c41bce40631a60fe401384004440fcdab085a","tid":108670,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢排moscow 機票有平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海嵾威除左歷史意義其實無咩好玩</blockquote><br />\n俄航？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個月查到三千頭左右來回<br />\n<br />\n得俄航有直飛。</blockquote><br />\n其實俄航服務點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好同差都聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俄航呢，機上娛樂同服務唔算好，但唔係差咁。餐食算ok。不過聽聞就係好多機司以前都係空軍，飛得好粗魯。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要舒服應該坐芬航去赫爾辛基再轉過去，坐 A350 (無查依家係咪全部轉晒)<br />\n<br />\n又新又舒服<br />\n<br />\n空姐應該都係香港人，全部講廣東話，無語言問題。"}]}